		<item>
		<title>龍与竜的區別</title>
		<link>/2019/02/14/9193.html</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Tcpicl]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Thu, 14 Feb 2019 14:25:30 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[龍學]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://69jj.wordpress.com/2019/02/14/%e9%be%8d%e4%b8%8e%e7%ab%9c%e7%9a%84%e5%8d%80%e5%88%a5/</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[龍与竜的读音都是龙[lóng]（此龙为简体字），繁体的龍字大家都很熟悉；年轻人对“竜”字也并不陌生，&#8230; <a href="/2019/02/14/9193.html" class="more-link read-more" rel="bookmark">继续阅读 <span class="screen-reader-text">龍与竜的區別</span><i class="fa fa-arrow-right"></i></a>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:19px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:.2px;orphans:2text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;display:inline !important;float:none;text-align:left;">龍与竜的读音都是龙[lóng]（此龙为简体字），繁体的龍字大家都很熟悉；年轻人对“竜”字也并不陌生，日本的动画片里常出现这个字，比如《七龙珠》，而“竜”字实实在在是个中国字。两者是什么关系呢？</span></p>
<p class="contentText contentSize contentPadding" style="margin:0.25rem0px0px;padding:0px17px;border:0;outline:0;vertical-align:baseline;background:0px0pxrgb(255,255,255);text-size-adjust:100%;overflow:visible;letter-spacing:.2px;font-size:.19rem;line-height:.3rem;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;orphans:2text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;">“龍”有五趾，而“竜”有四趾（有时候是三趾）。</p>
<p class="contentText contentSize contentPadding" style="margin:0.25rem0px0px;padding:0px17px;border:0;outline:0;vertical-align:baseline;background:0px0pxrgb(255,255,255);text-size-adjust:100%;overflow:visible;letter-spacing:.2px;font-size:.19rem;line-height:.3rem;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;orphans:2text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;">正如凤凰的“凤”是雄，“凰”是雌；麒麟的“麒”对应雄，“麟”对应雌。龙的汉字也分”龍“和“竜”两种，龍代表雄性，竜代表雌性。</p>
<p><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:19px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:.2px;orphans:2text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;display:inline !important;float:none;text-align:left;">在清朝以前的中国，只有中国的皇帝能用画有雄性龍的旗。属国日本和朝鲜的天皇等只被允许用画有雌性“竜”的旗，所以日本和朝鲜的“竜”都没有五根脚趾。</span><br />
<span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:19px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:.2px;orphans:2text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;display:inline !important;float:none;text-align:left;">在伟岸的奇异美感里，龙还充溢着内在之美。在上古人们的想象中，龙有许多种如应龙、蛱龙、螭等，但都生活在水里，是雨水之神。而雨水与云雾密切相关，所以龙能乘云驾雾。</span></p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
